Note: Bar (Musical Measure) Standard Library
Note: Provides functions for creating and manipulating musical bars

Note: ===== Core Bar Operations =====

Note: Creates an empty bar
internal proc createBar()

Note: Creates a bar with a single note
internal proc createBarWithNote(Note: note)

Note: Creates a bar from an array of notes
internal proc createBarFromNotes(Notes: notes)

Note: Adds a note to an existing bar (mutates the bar)
internal proc addNoteToBar(Bar: bar, Note: note)

Note: Gets a note from a bar at the specified index
internal proc getNoteFromBar(Bar: bar, Int: index)

Note: Gets the number of notes in a bar
internal proc barLength(Bar: bar)

Note: Sets the time signature for a bar
internal proc setTimeSignature(Bar: bar, Int: numerator, Int: denominator)

Note: Gets the time signature of a bar as a string (e.g., "4/4")
internal proc getTimeSignature(Bar: bar)
